snippet.title: Deep Sea - Trailer
snippet.description:
Deep Sea is a live-action interactive film. You will be involved in the investigation of a bizarre crime. Your choices will determine the life or death of a person, the fate of a group, doubt or trust, redemption or escape, during the game you will gradually feel the choice.
Developer : 舞刀弄影 and 舒尔佳
Publisher : INDIECN
